content.html: As much as I wish it were, I do not think male birth control (including vasectomies) is a practical solution. In fact, I think it would make this health crisis worse. Why? It's simple: men would lie to get out of wearing a condom. And their partners wouldn't know to take EC.
content.value:
As much as I wish it were, I do not think male birth control (including vasectomies) is a practical solution.

In fact, I think it would make this health crisis worse.

Why? It's simple: men would lie to get out of wearing a condom. And their partners wouldn't know to take EC.
